00:10:40.290 --> 00:10:41.590
&gt;&gt; Laila Lalami: Yeah, yeah.

00:10:41.590 --> 00:10:42.890
I mean, and this is the thing.

00:10:42.890 --> 00:10:46.450 position:56%
When I came across the story, I had
